      "body": "> I wonder what would be the best approach to solve this.\n\nThe `CChainParams::SigNet` factory method takes an optional `SigNetOptions` struct, so it should be fairly straightforward to add an optional `signet_challenge` parameter to `btck_chain_parameters_create`?",
